{"tid":259562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子買外賣　iPhone被擸走","createTime":"2017-05-27T04:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T06:09:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"091bd0c94096b75375ad62d1e8160fb80c934e7c","tid":259562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035357&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035357%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&d=d66SdBlJp1VENnazzFlDUzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b37055a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035357%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&h=b46eeac1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035357&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527</a><br />\n<br />\n女子買外賣　iPhone被擸走<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名女子日前在沙田一間茶餐廳買外賣時，將手機遺留在收銀櫃枱前，結果遭另一名付賬女子順手牽羊取走，案發過程遭CCTV全程拍下，女事主其後報警，警方正追緝涉案女子調查。<br />\n被人偷走iPhone7 Plus手機的女事主姓楊，25歲，她接受《蘋果》訪問時表示被偷手機約值8,000元，是5日前才購買。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n事主買外賣遺下iPhone7 Plus手機（左圖），事後遭另一女子取走（右圖）。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n警員安慰「睇開啲」<br />\n<br />\n本周三中午12時許，楊女與友人到沙田河畔花園一餐廳買外賣，她付款時將手機交託予女友人保管，但友人卻順手將手機放在收銀櫃枱面，二人忘記取回手機便站在一旁等候食物，未幾一名短髮女子走近收銀櫃枱結賬，當時她看到枱面擺放一部iPhone7 Plus手機，付賬後即順手取走手機離開，整個過程大約一分鐘。<br />\n楊女其後發現手機不翼而飛，立刻向茶餐廳職員查詢，經翻看CCTV確認被人盜走，同日傍晚6時報警。她引述警方稱案件較難搜證，並有警員安慰她「睇開啲」，警方現正追緝一名年約40至50歲、肥胖身材蓄短髮的涉案女子。<br />\n■記者莫家文<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=d66SdBlJp1VENnazzFlDUzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9e2a818c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"829af1c7abc83f45889fe5bdec501ef157c2a57d","tid":259562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"事主買外賣遺下iPhone7 Plus手機（左圖），事後遭另一女子取走（右圖）。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170527/large/27la8p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170527%2Flarge%2F27la8p03.jpg&h=e19deec8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bb30c46dc67e250d85a70bbebf340dbf1d4f0e5","tid":259562,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">她付款時將手機交託予女友人保管，但友人卻順手將手機放在收銀櫃枱面</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1bfa332f8abd069768dd8fe07ff567f1651826","tid":259562,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">她付款時將手機交託予女友人保管，但友人卻順手將手機放在收銀櫃枱面</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcba3fe757d30ad7a215ad4d8fc0ff4b78fd78c","tid":2